This topic explains how to install <%= vars.ops_manager_first %> on GCP using Terraform.


## <a id='overview'></a> Overview

You can install <%= vars.ops_manager %> on GCP with either the <%= vars.app_runtime_first %> or <%= vars.k8s_runtime_first %> runtime.

To install <%= vars.ops_manager %> on GCP using Terraform, do one of the following:

* Install with <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %>. For more information, see [Install on <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %> Using Terraform](#terraform-pas) below.

* Install with <%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %>. For more information, see [Install on <%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %> Using Terraform](#terraform-pks) below.


## <a id='terraform-pas'></a> Install with <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %> Using Terraform

To install with <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %> using Terraform:

1. Deploy <%= vars.ops_manager %>. For more information, see [Deploying <%= vars.ops_manager %> on GCP Using Terraform](../gcp/prepare-env-terraform.html).

1. Configure BOSH Director. For more information, see [Configuring BOSH Director on GCP Using Terraform](../gcp/config-terraform.html).

1. (Optional) Configure a shared VPC. For more information, see [(Optional) Configuring a Shared VPC on GCP](gcp-shared-vpc.html).


## <a id='terraform-pks'></a> Install with <%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %> Using Terraform

To install with <%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %> using Terraform:

1. Deploy <%= vars.ops_manager %>. For more information, see [Deploying <%= vars.ops_manager %> on GCP Using Terraform](../gcp/prepare-env-terraform.html).

1. Configure BOSH Director. For more information, see [Configuring BOSH Director on GCP Using Terraform](../gcp/config-terraform.html).

1. (Optional). Configure a shared VPC. For more information, see [(Optional) Configuring a Shared VPC on GCP](gcp-shared-vpc.html).


